         <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p> . . . ] great great great grandson [of deified Trajan, victor in Parthia and of deified Nerva, 
               Marcus] Aurelius [Antoninus Pius Felix Augustus, greatest victor in Parthia, greatest victor in Britannia, greatest victor in Germany,] chief priest, holding tribunician power 
               [for the nineteenth time, acclaimed victor three times, consul four times], father of the country, [proconsul. Milestone thirty]-nine.</p></div>
         
